snippet.title: MVP 07 NCAA Baseball (PS2) - Intro
snippet.description: The intro cinematic for MVP 07 NCAA Baseball, a college baseball video game for PlayStation 2. The broadcasters are Mike Patrick and Kyle Peterson.
